{"tid":1471964,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB九線偽人谷微撐警「譴責暴徒」","createTime":"2019-08-14T12:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T02:26:53.000Z","uid":256585,"like":61,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"04a640d16a7cba9614668d70d52f1589c7047cc2","tid":1471964,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wiDyL13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwiDyL13.png&h=2e63f22d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jJhS1Ar.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjJhS1Ar.png&h=9eb4d785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n收皮啦大陸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2PH38fs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2PH38fs.png&h=9a744b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翻查紀錄谷微正正係垃圾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">新移民</span>落嚟香港搶資源<br />\n<br />\n撈唔掂又改個新名扮新人<br />\n<br />\n廣東話講唔正仲成日喺度拍埋啲垃圾抖音<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">極度可恥<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n點解撐我地嘅林秀怡林泳淘就要雪<br />\n<br />\n藍絲谷微又唔洗收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要求大台好應該一視同仁<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">強烈建議懲罰埋谷微將佢永久雪藏</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一人一封去信投訴佢<br />\n<br />\n[url]tvbpr@tvb.com.hk[/url]"},{"pid":"aabb3bec44e3cbee9407195471d5b48fdda525bc","tid":1471964,"uid":256585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:07:44.000Z","msg":"tvbpr@tvb.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n顯示唔到個email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b4247d16d0b88f615602ac47b104ab350e1d8c","tid":1471964,"uid":7849,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"Who?<img src=\"/assets